1. Moj *ujak* je inženjer. (My *uncle* is an engineer.)
2. Na *ujakovom* imanju ima mnogo voća. (There is a lot of fruit on *my uncle's* estate.)
3. Ana i Luka su bili kod *ujaka*. (Ana and Luka went to visit *uncle*.)
4. *Ujaci* su mi iz Vojvodine. (My *uncles* are from Vojvodina.)
5. Njegov *ujak* je bio pilot u Drugom svetskom ratu. (His *uncle* was a pilot in World War II.)
6. *Ujaku* je drago što dolaziš na slavu. ( *Uncle* is happy that you are coming to the celebration.)
7. *Ujaka* često viđam u parku sa svojim psom. (I often see *uncle* in the park with his dog.)
8. Ivana se svađa sa svojim *ujakom* oko nasleđa. (Ivana is arguing with her *uncle* about the inheritance.)
9. *Ujaci* su kupili novu kuću na selu. (My *uncles* bought a new house in the countryside.)
10. *Ujaku* se dopada moja nova frizura. (*Uncle* likes my new hairstyle.)